HEADWORD: Processioning
<hw>Pro*ces"sion*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A proceeding prescribed by
statute for ascertaining and fixing the boundaries of land. See 2d
<er>Procession</er>.</def> <mark>[ Local, U. S.]</mark>
<rj><au>Bouvier.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
